@startuml
title ETR Study API — Slot transitions on review (reference SchedulePolicy etr_methodology_four_slot v1.0.0)

' Conventions:
'   tags: easy / hard / forgot
'   easy   = advance one slot (and inside D, advance ladder rung)
'   hard   = step back one slot (A stays at A)
'   forgot = reset to A
'   delays in the reference policy are listed in the spec page transition table
'   (PT1H / P1D / P3D / P7D / P14D / P30D / P60D ...).

[*] --> A : new conspectus\n(seeded by createConspectus)

A : delay on entry: PT1H (first retrieve)
B : delay on entry: P1D
C : delay on entry: P3D
D : delay on entry: ladder rung\nD[0]=P7D D[1]=P14D D[2]=P30D ...

A --> B : easy
A --> A : hard / forgot
B --> C : easy
B --> A : hard
B --> A : forgot
C --> D : easy / ladder_index = 0
C --> B : hard
C --> A : forgot
D --> D : easy / ladder_index += 1
D --> C : hard / ladder_index = 0
D --> A : forgot / ladder_index = 0

@enduml
